## ğŸ§® Example Utility Functions (utils.py)

```python
from datetime import date, timedelta

def today_utc_date():
    return date.today()

def start_of_week(today):
    return today - timedelta(days=today.weekday())

def start_of_month(today):
    return today.replace(day=1)
```

